nte el pasado español de Valdés. Las epifanías de los personajes confirman que el modelo de lengua castellana 'cortesana' que Valdés bosqueja es una exigencia que sienten los mismos italianos.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertVervuert Complete eBook-Package 2021z9783110743340oZDB-207-IBV40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869230240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968692302423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968692302/original  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-207-IBVb2021